Package: benchfigR
Title: NC-Style Benchmark and Biological Case Figure Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Jiang", family = "Congxin", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jcx981212@163.com")
Author: Jiang Congxin
Maintainer: Jiang Congxin <jcx981212@163.com>
Description: R toolkit for training and generating NC-style benchmark plus biological case figures from traceable metric, rank, runtime, robustness, and case source-data tables. It builds on ncfigR for shared theme, benchmark heatmap, embedding, composition, and export conventions.
